    "As director, he oversaw the shows \"Pharaohs: Treasures of Egyptian Art from the Louvre,\" \"Faberge in America,\" and \"Vatican Treasures: Early Christian, Renaissance and Baroque Art from the Papal Collections\" the last of which he co-curated.": [],
